Class AdminPage

    public class AdminPage
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    The AdminPage class represents Control page. It provides all the control that admin or highest Rank warden can access.

    Admin Page has following Controls For Prisoner : 

          Add a Prisoner.
                Find a Prisoner.
                Release a Prisoner.
                Delete a Prisoner.
                Update Prisoner's Details.
                Genrate Reports of all Prisoner.

    Admin Page has following Controls For Warden : 

          Add a Warden.
                Find a Warden.
                Delete a Warden.
                Update Warden's Details.
                Genrate Reports of all Warden.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
